Steps for running Glim

ros2 run glim_ros glim_rosnode

#If not configured in the src
ros2 run glim_ros glim_rosnode --ros-args -p config_path:=$(realpath ~/config)

If you edit the config in the ~/ros2_ws/src/glim folder then when you build the app and re-source ros you can just use "ros2 run glim_ros glim_rosnode" for the config
